      "writtenOn": "2026-04-27T10:51:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why a new binary? Can\u0027t the various types not share one binary and then select via `argv[1]` which code path is run?\n\nI would expect the total compressed size of the binaries to be less if it was combined into one binary or even combined with existing state manager binary.\n\nMerging things like that already resulted in compressed size reduction of the bmcweb.",
