      "message": "IMO process crash is not in scope for consideration. Why would we design for our code to crash? If there is a bug we can fix it?\n\nAnd what do you mean with \u0027upgrade\u0027?\n\nDo you mean updating individual packages on the BMC and restarting them individually?",
